code: @Override public Processor createProcessor(RouteContext routeContext) throws Exception {     if (definition.getMessageFrequency() != null) {         return new SamplingThrottler(definition.getMessageFrequency()).     } else {         // should default be 1 sample period         long time = definition.getSamplePeriod() != null ? definition.getSamplePeriod() : 1L.         // should default be in seconds         TimeUnit tu = definition.getUnits() != null ? definition.getUnits() : TimeUnit.SECONDS.         return new SamplingThrottler(time, tu).     } }
